<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:06:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗和黎巴嫩的暗杀事件将中东推向地区战争的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-in-iran-and-lebanon-pushed-mideast-to-the-edge-of-a-regional-war/00000191-07e5-dd56-a9f5-6fe743d30000</link><description>以色列尚未对伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在德黑兰遇刺事件承担正式责任，但伊朗不太可能对发生在自己领土上的袭击置之不理。哈尼亚被杀也减少了人质交易谈判取得突破的机会</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:57:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-in-iran-and-lebanon-pushed-mideast-to-the-edge-of-a-regional-war/00000191-07e5-dd56-a9f5-6fe743d30000</guid></item><item><title>军事法庭延长对八名涉嫌性虐待加沙被拘留者的士兵的逮捕期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/military-court-extends-arrest-of-8-soldiers-suspected-of-sexually-abusing-gazan-detainee/00000191-07c2-d3e8-adbd-bfd69e370000</link><description>八名士兵的拘留已延长至周日。据称，他们属于 Sde Teiman 的“核心圈子”，对虐待事件知情，但对于巴勒斯坦被拘留者在他们看守期间如何受伤给出了相互矛盾的解释</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/military-court-extends-arrest-of-8-soldiers-suspected-of-sexually-abusing-gazan-detainee/00000191-07c2-d3e8-adbd-bfd69e370000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称哈尼亚暗杀“懦弱”，世界对他的死感到震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/iran-says-haniyeh-assassination-cowardly-as-world-reacts-with-shock-to-his-death/00000191-0795-d3e8-adbd-bfd7d05b0000</link><description>哈马斯政治领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在伊朗中部被杀后，外交部和政府发言人迅速发出谴责，称这是“危险的升级”。尽管美国没有谴责或庆祝，但他们发誓要保护以色列免受袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/iran-says-haniyeh-assassination-cowardly-as-world-reacts-with-shock-to-his-death/00000191-0795-d3e8-adbd-bfd7d05b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队任命备受争议的巴拉克·希拉姆将军为加沙师指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-appoints-controversial-general-barak-hiram-to-commander-of-gaza-division/00000191-07ae-dd56-a9f5-6fefb7420000</link><description>10 月 7 日，希勒姆指挥的部队向贝埃里基布兹的一处民宅发射了坦克炮弹，里面有人质。尽管一些贝埃里家族对这一决定存在分歧，但海勒姆相信他最适合担任这一职务</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-appoints-controversial-general-barak-hiram-to-commander-of-gaza-division/00000191-07ae-dd56-a9f5-6fefb7420000</guid></item><item><title>在德黑兰被暗杀的哈马斯政治领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/hamas-confirms-its-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran/00000191-06d9-d117-abd9-8ffff56e0000</link><description>该恐怖组织表示，哈尼亚在参加伊朗新总统的宣誓就职仪式后，在“犹太复国主义分子对他在德黑兰的住所进行的一次危险的袭击”中被杀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/hamas-confirms-its-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran/00000191-06d9-d117-abd9-8ffff56e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡只能从袭击以色列国防军两个基地的混乱分子中获益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-only-stands-to-gain-from-the-agents-of-chaos-who-stormed-two-idf-bases/00000191-0531-df85-a399-ed37094d0000</link><description>将两个军事基地的暴力袭击与特拉维夫的民主示威活动（以色列总理似乎所做的那样）进行比较，引起了我们自 10 月 7 日以来从未经历过的担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-only-stands-to-gain-from-the-agents-of-chaos-who-stormed-two-idf-bases/00000191-0531-df85-a399-ed37094d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人哈尼亚在德黑兰被杀后，伊朗最高领导人誓言对以色列进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-live/idf-hezbollah-fired-20-rockets-at-northern-israel-sparking-widespread-fire/00000191-069d-dc27-abdb-f6fd48370000</link><description>以色列在约旦河西岸发生刺伤事件后伤势严重 ■ “卑鄙行径：”巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯谴责在德黑兰杀害哈马斯领导人汉尼耶 ■ 以色列关闭哈德拉以北领空 ■ 国防部长奥斯汀表示中东战争并非不可避免，美国将保卫以色列如果遭到袭击 军事法庭延长对涉嫌性虐待加沙被拘留者的 8 名士兵的逮捕 黎巴嫩卫生部：以色列对贝鲁特的空袭造成 4 人死亡、74 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 02:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-live/idf-hezbollah-fired-20-rockets-at-northern-israel-sparking-widespread-fire/00000191-069d-dc27-abdb-f6fd48370000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/00000191-054c-d130-a5bf-b5ce54e30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:21:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/00000191-054c-d130-a5bf-b5ce54e30000</guid></item><item><title>死者家属会见以色列国防军指挥官，指挥官下令用坦克向贝埃里基布兹的家开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</link><description>基布兹的一份声明称，大多数受害者家属在结束对话时都感到和解，并对哈马斯袭击期间的情况有了更好的了解。会议几小时后，以色列国防军宣布任命他为加沙师指挥官</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 19:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</guid></item><item><title>“他们向我吐口水，称我为荡妇”：记者在以色列国防军基地遭到极右暴徒袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</link><description>周一，右翼抗议者对前来报道斯德泰曼拘留中心袭击事件的一些以色列记者进行辱骂、吐口水和人身攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</guid></item><item><title>要成为一个文明国家，以色列必须承认自己的野蛮行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡不能两全其美。他不能试图将以色列描绘成一个开明的民主国家，保卫自己（和西方世界）免受残酷怪物的侵害，同时也容忍那些不认为应该调查针对可能的恐怖分子的野蛮行为的部长</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 298 天：以色列国防军称其目标是真主党二号人物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</link><description>以色列平民被黎巴嫩火箭弹弹片炸死 ■ 以色列国防军消息人士称，被扣押在加沙的一些人质尸体将永远找不到袭击以色列国防军基地的右翼暴徒 ■ 据报道，英国已决定推迟停止向以色列出口武器的决定 ■ 战争进入 298 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</guid></item><item><title>看到受虐待的加沙被拘留者的斯德·泰曼医生：“我不敢相信以色列狱警能做出这样的事”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/doctor-who-saw-abused-gazan-detainee-i-couldnt-believe-an-israeli-jailer-could-do-this/00000191-0436-df85-a399-ed36f4800000</link><description>斯德泰曼医院的医生约尔·唐钦教授在这名加沙被拘留者据称遭到九名以色列预备役军人虐待后见过他，他对该男子的状况表示震惊。 “我确信这是努赫巴人对努赫巴人的报复，”他说，指的是哈马斯精英部队</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:42:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/doctor-who-saw-abused-gazan-detainee-i-couldnt-believe-an-israeli-jailer-could-do-this/00000191-0436-df85-a399-ed36f4800000</guid></item><item><title>高级警官对以色列国防军基地的骚乱表示：“明确的政策是视而不见”； “本-格维尔不必说一句话”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/senior-police-officers-on-riots-at-idf-bases-the-clear-policy-was-to-turn-a-blind-eye/00000191-03c8-d117-abd9-8fef5fea0000</link><description>高级警察批评以色列警察部队在应对周一斯德泰曼和拜特利德骚乱时的行为，允许抗议者闯入基地。一位高级官员表示，“警察已经破产，没有指挥”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/senior-police-officers-on-riots-at-idf-bases-the-clear-policy-was-to-turn-a-blind-eye/00000191-03c8-d117-abd9-8fef5fea0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日之后：以色列考古学家创造了在战区寻找人类遗骸的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/after-oct-7-israeli-archaeologists-create-methodology-to-find-human-remains-in-war-zones/00000191-03f7-d3e8-adbd-bbf71c5d0000</link><description>当以色列考古学家在哈马斯袭击后加入搜寻失踪人员的行列时，他们运用了独特的训练方法，在遭到破坏、烧毁的地区寻找失踪的尸体。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/after-oct-7-israeli-archaeologists-create-methodology-to-find-human-remains-in-war-zones/00000191-03f7-d3e8-adbd-bbf71c5d0000</guid></item><item><title>“战争从来没有拯救过儿童。大多数德鲁兹人表示，他们不希望自己的悲剧引发更多杀戮”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-30/ty-article-podcast/war-never-saved-children-most-druze-dont-want-their-tragedy-to-cause-more-killing/00000191-0322-da0d-afd1-8bae4b7c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-30/ty-article-podcast/war-never-saved-children-most-druze-dont-want-their-tragedy-to-cause-more-killing/00000191-0322-da0d-afd1-8bae4b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部真主党猛攻后，一名男子被火箭弹碎片炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-by-rocket-shrapnel-in-northern-israel-following-hezbollah-barrage/00000191-03e8-d117-abd9-8fef2bef0000</link><description>两天前，戈兰高地 Majdal Shams 镇发生火箭弹袭击，导致 12 名儿童和青少年丧生，以色列称该镇是真主党所为，28 岁的尼尔·普普科 (Nir Pupko) 被杀。以色列尚未对周六的袭击做出回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-by-rocket-shrapnel-in-northern-israel-following-hezbollah-barrage/00000191-03e8-d117-abd9-8fef2bef0000</guid></item><item><title>格兰特呼吁内塔尼亚胡调查本格维尔在警方对以色列国防军基地骚乱反应迟缓中所扮演的角色</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-netanyahu-probe-ben-gvirs-role-in-delayed-response-to-riots-at-idf-bases/00000191-0386-df85-a399-eb96270e0000</link><description>加兰特在一封信中告诉总理，“支持以色列国防军基地骚乱并积极参与骚乱的民选官员构成了损害国家安全的非常严重的危险”，敦促他“果断地解决这个问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-netanyahu-probe-ben-gvirs-role-in-delayed-response-to-riots-at-idf-bases/00000191-0386-df85-a399-eb96270e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对 Majdal Shams 有宏伟的计划。然后与真主党的战争开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-had-big-plans-for-majdal-shams-then-the-war-with-hezbollah-started/00000191-0388-d76c-abf3-d3eb8f550000</link><description>自叙利亚内战以来，戈兰高地德鲁兹派与以色列当局之间的关系有所升温，但加沙战争冻结了迈季代勒​​沙姆斯的计划，该镇周一遭到火箭袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-had-big-plans-for-majdal-shams-then-the-war-with-hezbollah-started/00000191-0388-d76c-abf3-d3eb8f550000</guid></item><item><title>如果真主党摧毁以色列的天然气钻井平台会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-would-happen-if-hezbollah-destroys-israels-natural-gas-rigs/00000191-0352-d76c-abf3-d37bda330000</link><description>如果北部局势升级，真主党可能会瞄准以色列的天然气钻井平台。三个钻机全部关闭的情况是极端的，但也是有可能的。煤炭可以弥补部分缺口，但还不够</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-would-happen-if-hezbollah-destroys-israels-natural-gas-rigs/00000191-0352-d76c-abf3-d37bda330000</guid></item></channel></rss>